SkiMaps
Price: $2.99
About
Maps
SkiMaps is a great iPhone app for skiers and snowboarders.
Download trail maps
to your iPhone and use the built-in GPS to find your way around the slopes.
You can even
send your location to friends
. Finding each other in the mountains has never been easier!
Track your activity
on the slopes and get graphs of your speed and vertical drop!
Check detailed
weather forecasts
and view
webcams
SkiMaps 2.7.1 is
available
!
Don't see your favorite ski resort in this list? Send us an email:
skimaps at planetreesoftware dot com
